== 0. Files

README		this file
Makefile	Makefile for libCSCSupervisor.so
Makefile.testapap Makefile for test applications
include/	include files for CSCSupervisor and EmuApplication
src/common/	source files for CSCSupervisor and EmuApplication
test/		files to test applications
   config.xml	XDAQ XML configuration file to run everyone on localhost
   bootxdaq	XDAQ executive boot shell script
   EmuFED/	dummy EmuFEDCrate application
   EmuPC/	dummy EmuPeripheralCrate application
   EmuDAQ/	dummy EmuDAQManager application
   EmuTF/	dummy TF_hyperDAQ application
   LTC/		dummy LTCControl application
   TTC/		dummy TTCciControl application

== 1. CVS access

foo> cd ~/work
foo> export CVSROOT=:pserver:anonymous@isscvs.cern.ch:/local/reps/tridas
foo> cvs login
...
foo> cvs co -r Release-3_0 -d cscSV TriDAS/emu/cscSV

== 2. Build and run

foo> cd cscSV
foo> export XDAQ_ROOT=/opt/xdaq
foo> export BUILD_HOME=..
foo> make install
foo> make -f Makefile.testapp install
foo> test/bootxdaq start

